(81, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Souveran 805 Stresemann Fine Point 鋼筆', 15.00, '2', '8', 'The foreign minister of the Weimar Republic, Gustav Stresemann (1879 - 1929), had an impressive political career. He also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit with stripes. He liked to wear suits with thin stripes and as life sometimes goes, a legend developed. Soon there after, people around the world called striped fountain pens, \"Stresemann\".; To officially acknowledge and honor his legend, Pelikan has now named the latest addition, the Souveran with elegant stripes in anthracite, the \"Stresemann\". ; Stresemann Features:; Anthracite stripes made of cellulose acetate on barrel Palladium plated clip and rings Hand-crafted finely engraved 18K gold nib available in extra-fine, fine medium or broad nib sizes. Delivered in a beautiful Pelikan gift box The Souveran 805 has an oversized body for those who enjoy a substantial pen.', '1', 'Souveran 805', '2', 0, 'pelikan_081-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(82, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Souveran 805 Stresemann Fine Point 鋼筆', 15.00, '3', '8', 'The foreign minister of the Weimar Republic, Gustav Stresemann (1879 - 1929), had an impressive political career. He also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit with stripes. He liked to wear suits with thin stripes and as life sometimes goes, a legend developed. Soon there after, people around the world called striped fountain pens, \"Stresemann\".; To officially acknowledge and honor his legend, Pelikan has now named the latest addition, the Souveran with elegant stripes in anthracite, the \"Stresemann\". ; Stresemann Features:; Anthracite stripes made of cellulose acetate on barrel Palladium plated clip and rings Hand-crafted finely engraved 18K gold nib available in extra-fine, fine medium or broad nib sizes. Delivered in a beautiful Pelikan gift box The Souveran 805 has an oversized body for those who enjoy a substantial pen.', '1', 'Souveran 805', '2', 0, 'pelikan_082-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(83, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes 鋼筆', 12.00, '1', '8', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes Fountain Pen, Extra-Fine Nib, Black, 1 Each is a true classic in fine writing made in Germany dedicated to the foreign minister of the German Weimarer Republic, Gustav Stresemann, who also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit. The elegant piston fountain pen is equipped with an 18-carat gold nib which is completely covered by rhodium to obtain a silver sheen. The barrel with the deceptively simple anthracite stripes is made of cellulose acetate, using a traditional process that is extremely work-intensive but gives this series its elegant character. Pen measures 13.3 cm with closed cap and weighs 16.4 grams. Easy to fill with no-mess Pelikan 4001 or Edelstein bottled ink.', '1', 'Souveran M605', '2', 0, 'pelikan_083-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(84, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes 鋼筆', 12.00, '2', '8', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes Fountain Pen, Extra-Fine Nib, Black, 1 Each is a true classic in fine writing made in Germany dedicated to the foreign minister of the German Weimarer Republic, Gustav Stresemann, who also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit. The elegant piston fountain pen is equipped with an 18-carat gold nib which is completely covered by rhodium to obtain a silver sheen. The barrel with the deceptively simple anthracite stripes is made of cellulose acetate, using a traditional process that is extremely work-intensive but gives this series its elegant character. Pen measures 13.3 cm with closed cap and weighs 16.4 grams. Easy to fill with no-mess Pelikan 4001 or Edelstein bottled ink.', '1', 'Souveran M605', '3', 0, 'pelikan_084-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(85, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes 鋼筆', 12.00, '3', '8', 'Pelikan Souverän M605 Stresemann Anthracite Stripes Fountain Pen, Extra-Fine Nib, Black, 1 Each is a true classic in fine writing made in Germany dedicated to the foreign minister of the German Weimarer Republic, Gustav Stresemann, who also became famous for the creation of a new kind of suit. The elegant piston fountain pen is equipped with an 18-carat gold nib which is completely covered by rhodium to obtain a silver sheen. The barrel with the deceptively simple anthracite stripes is made of cellulose acetate, using a traditional process that is extremely work-intensive but gives this series its elegant character. Pen measures 13.3 cm with closed cap and weighs 16.4 grams. Easy to fill with no-mess Pelikan 4001 or Edelstein bottled ink.', '1', 'Souveran M605', '3', 0, 'pelikan_085-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(86, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Pura P40鋼筆', 13.00, '2', '6', 'Pelikan Pura P40 Fountain Pen, Broad Nib, Silver, 1 Each boasts a discreetly elegant silhouette. A balanced combination of matte and shiny surfaces. The solid, spring-loaded chrome-plated clip on the cap subtly accentuates the straight-lined shape design of the pen. Pen length is 138 cm and weighs 35 grams. Works with a practical cartridge refill system and Pelikan cartridges are recommended. Made in Germany.', '3', 'Pura P40', '3', 0, 'pelikan_086-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(87, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Pura P40鋼筆', 13.00, '3', '6', 'Pelikan Pura P40 Fountain Pen, Broad Nib, Silver, 1 Each boasts a discreetly elegant silhouette. A balanced combination of matte and shiny surfaces. The solid, spring-loaded chrome-plated clip on the cap subtly accentuates the straight-lined shape design of the pen. Pen length is 138 cm and weighs 35 grams. Works with a practical cartridge refill system and Pelikan cartridges are recommended. Made in Germany.', '3', 'Pura P40', '3', 0, 'pelikan_087-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(88, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Pura P40鋼筆', 13.00, '2', '6', 'Pelikan Pura P40 Fountain Pen, Broad Nib, Black/Silver, 1 Each combines modern elegance with reliable functionality. By combining shiny and frosted surfaces, an interesting contrast between bright silver and classic blue has been created. Works with a practical cartridge refill system and Pelikan cartridges are recommended. Pen length is 13.8 cm and weighs 35 grams. Made in Germany.', '17', 'Pura P40', '2', 0, 'pelikan_088-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(89, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Pura P40鋼筆', 13.00, '3', '6', 'Pelikan Pura P40 Fountain Pen, Broad Nib, Black/Silver, 1 Each combines modern elegance with reliable functionality. By combining shiny and frosted surfaces, an interesting contrast between bright silver and classic blue has been created. Works with a practical cartridge refill system and Pelikan cartridges are recommended. Pen length is 13.8 cm and weighs 35 grams. Made in Germany.', '17', 'Pura P40', '2', 0, 'pelikan_089-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
(90, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Edelstein Moonstone M205 鋼筆', 11.00, '2', '6', 'Pelikan 特別版 Tradition M205 月光石鋼筆,超細筆尖,1 支,每支筆都有魔法灰色,提醒月光光線,一旦筆接觸到日光,就會閃閃發光。 德國製造,具有吸引力和表現力的書寫工具。 採用 1929 年推出的第一款差異活塞機制。 筆長度為 12.5 公分,重量為 14 克。 輕鬆填充,不會弄髒的 Pelikan Edelstein Moonstone 墨水或其他的 4001 和 Edelstein 墨水(墨水另售)。', '4', 'Tradition M205', '1', 0, 'pelikan_090-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
