(102, '', 2, 'pelikan', 'Pelikan Pelikano Up Ice Blue', 1.00, '2', '5', 'Pelikano Up - upgrade your handwriting! High-quality, aluminium metal fountain pen with attractive clip design. With soft grip for fatigue-free writing. Left and right handed models available. Made in Germany.', '11', 'Pelikano  Ice Blue', '1', 0, 'pelikan_102-1.jpg', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1),
